### Summary

| Aspect | Magic Tower (法师塔) | Barracks (兵营) |
|---|---|---|
| **Rotation** | Rotates to face target via `RotateTowardsTarget()` | **Does not rotate** — explicitly skipped |
| **Attack mechanism** | Fires `FireMagicAttack()` (projectile with `DamageType.Magic`) | Spawns soldiers at rally point |
| **Key script** | `TowerAttack.cs`, `Projectile.cs` | `BarracksAttack.cs`, `Soldier.cs` |
| **Cooldown** | Uses standard cooldown (`1f / stats.attackSpeed`) | No cooldown (soldiers are persistent) |
| **Targeting** | Tower itself aims at enemies in range | Soldiers auto-assign from rally point |

The Barracks is the *only* tower type explicitly excluded from rotation. All other types including Mage follow the same rotation logic in `Tower.cs`.
